						               													<description>A box full of surprises, three exciting time travel adventures and a unique combination of quiz questions and escape feeling - that's QUIZscape! The game box is a time machine with which the players must complete three adventures. The novel game concept by Arno Steinwender alternates various puzzles with quiz questions: Wrong answers increase the time pressure! And the game is full of surprises.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The 1st adventure takes the players to Victorian London. The author of the Sherlock Holmes novels has disappeared and the players must find him again.&amp;#10;The 2nd adventure is set in ancient Egypt. The players try to gain Cleopatra's trust and bring the secret scrolls to safety.&amp;#10;In the 3rd adventure, players follow in the footsteps of the greatest universal genius of all time: Leonardo da Vinci.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is suitable for beginners and offers a quick start. Everyone can start puzzling right away in just a few steps.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;How to play:&amp;#10;The players play together through 3 different adventures. In the process, they have to answer quiz questions and solve puzzles. Additional clues and secret messages are hidden in the box. But be careful: time is running out, and time is deducted for each incorrectly answered quiz question. &amp;#10;Can the players find the clues and solve the questions and puzzles?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
